{
  "stem": "22685.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we have-- and we are passing again Russia because they occupied part of that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we have-- we had the same-- again, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It took me thousands miles to go away, hundreds of miles to go away from them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We ended up in Romania.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was a camp in [ROMANIAN], the name of the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "After a few months, a friend of mine came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were talking-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was decided we are going to go-- I mean, he was able to take us from Romania to Austria to the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then we are going to worry later on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But the, the funny part is the papers that we made-- we made ourselves the papers-- the same papers from Poland to Romania, we made ourselves.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had stamps, all kind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "In Russia what is important is a round stamp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We had round stamps there, so-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and so, so we made papers that-- to go from Hungary to Romania.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But the papers, we went from Romania to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Anyhow, we passed the Hungarian border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then we came to Austria, to Graz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "This was the major center of the Russian occupation zone in Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Austria had three occupation zones, Russian-- I mean, Russian-- four-- Russian, American, British, and French.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We ended up in that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The only problem, problem was to go from the Russian zone to any other zone from the not desirable British, but it depends, and from there into Italy.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then it was hopefully to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But when we came, the border was closed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So my friend, that-- which I met in, in [ROMANIAN]-- we took two bottles of vodka.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We took a little suitcase.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We went on the border.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "The Russians should arrest us.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
